===Alternative forms===
Note that in traditional Chinese, the component [[File:U26c29-ue0102.svg|25px|text-bottom|𦰩󠄂|link=𦰩]] for this character is written with [[廿]] on top while in Japanese [[wikipedia:Shinjitai|shinjitai]], the component [[File:U26c29.svg|25px|text-bottom|𦰩|link=𦰩]] is written with [[艹]] on top and has one stroke less. In simplified Chinese, the component [[File:U26c29-ue0102.svg|25px|text-bottom|𦰩󠄂|link=𦰩]] is simplified to [[又]] instead.

===Usage notes===
In [[wikipedia:Classical Chinese|classical Chinese]], this character is used [[interchangeably]] with [[歎]] to express a [[sigh]] or [[lament]].

